Package: dbGaPprep
Title: Creates and Checks Standard Files for dbGaP submission
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Nelson", "Sarah", email = "sarahcn@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package can create or check dataset and data dictionary files for the required dbGaP submission elements: sample-subject mapping, sample attributes, and subject consent files. Optionally, pedigree and phenotpye files can be checked for presence of expected subjects. (say something about TOPMed as motivating use case to create?)
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
